name: Fathomless (Mr. Admirals)
description:
Fathomless is a 2D top-to-bottom scroller where the player must avoid hazards as they guide the Scubanaut on a surreal journey through the depths. As the Scubanaut descends, so does the strangeness and the confusion.

Development Time: 48 hours

Release Date: October 2017

Programmers: 

  • David King
  • Keenan Barber

Artists

  • Mary Benetti
  • Jonathan Worman
  • Grant Hyslop

NOTE: Ensure you are using a WebGL capable browser to run the game properly
